speech.p:
Resolved,
That the Orders made by the Secretary of State for the Home Department under the

Sunday Entertainments Act, 1932, extending Section 1 of the Act to—


(1) the Urban Borough of Bridgwater;

(2) the Urban District of Letchworth;

(3) the Parish of Mildenhall in the Rural District of Mildenhall;

(4) the Borough of Stretford;

(5) the Borough of Wanstead and Wood-ford; and

(6) the Parish of Westerham in the Rural District of Sevenoaks


copies of which were presented to this House on 13th November, be approved."—[Major Dugdale.]
